  "original_title": "\u0b9f\u0bca\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baf\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b95\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bc8 - \u0baa\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0b95 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0ba9 \u0b9a\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Don Priasat's brother killed in Wellampittia - drug trade dispute suspected",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "A person has been hacked to death by two people on a motorcycle near Mempalam - Orukodavath under Wellampittia Police Division.",
        "The police said that 34-year-old Prakash Dilina Kumara of Meethottamullai-Kalangsuriya area, who is the brother of Don Priyasad, who is considered to be an activist of a Sinhala hardline organization, was killed in this way. This incident was reported yesterday (25) night.",
        "The police said that usually at night, the person spends time with his friends near the Orukodavath flyover, but on one such occasion, two men on a motorcycle hacked him to death with a sharp weapon.",
        "The police said that the murdered person had previously been released on bail after being remanded for the charge of assaulting and injuring several people with sharp weapons, but he signed the court order every month at the Wellampittia police station.",
        "According to the initial investigations carried out by the Wellampitti police regarding this murder, evidences have been revealed which suspect that the murder was a result of drug trade and further investigations are being carried out."
      ],
